            <h2>
                <b><i>Airborn.co</i></b> is a free takeoff and landing distance calculator
            </h2>

            <p class="fs-5">
                Airborn.co is a free, <a href="https://github.com/alexjcampbell/airborn/">open source project</a>,
                that sets out to take the pain out of learning how to do takeoff and landing calculations.

            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
