<br />
<p>This app was motivated by the idea that folks are more likely to actually do takeoff and landing
    calculations
    if there's an app that can quickly do the work for them, rather than digging through the POH and doing
    multiple interpolations.</p>

<p>This is the v0.2 release, which performs basic takeoff and landing distance calculations for every runway at a given
    airport, for a given airplane, in a given set of conditions.</p>
<p>Airport and runway Data is courtesy of the folks at <a href="https://ourairports.com/data/">Our
        Airports</a>.
</p>
